    "Finally, Iftikhar et al. (2024) and Zhang et al. (2025) explored the disparities between LLM-and human-led CBT sessions, highlighting gaps such as empathy and cultural nuance while also introducing CBT-Bench to probe LLMs' deeper psychotherapeutic competencies.",
